{"tid":2223355,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陸偉雄: 表證不成立即係控方連最基本嘅控罪元素都證明唔到","createTime":"2020-09-29T18:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T06:48:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8ada43d2b2df8be2eb52a5fb2d830bdd0bff2c","tid":2223355,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"何謂「表面證供成立（case to answer）」？大律師陸偉雄解釋審訊分成兩階段，首階段由控方舉證，鋪陳人證物證，若證據表面上看來並非不可靠、不齊全或缺乏根據，法庭便裁定表證成立，但距定罪還有一段距離。陸指若連表證也不成立，「即係控方連最基本嘅控罪元素都證明唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n陸以暴動罪為例，控罪元素包括被告有共同目的而集結，並作出破壞社會安寧的行為。法庭需考慮被告當時的言行舉動，能否構成犯案的推論基礎，例如「記者喺現場合法採訪就明顯冇共同目的」；若社工或神職人員在場「好心叫人快啲走」，亦難屬犯法，「因為做嘅嘢同本身職責有關。」當表證成立後，才進入第二階段，即被告答辯，他可出庭作供、傳召證人或呈交證據等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/WPZWOZWUCFHZLDVS2P6CA66VOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FWPZWOZWUCFHZLDVS2P6CA66VOY%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWL%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=4b328634\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FWPZWOZWUCFHZLDVS2P6CA66VOY%2F&h=04fa7219\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/WPZWOZWUCFHZLDVS2P6CA66VOY/</a>"},{"pid":"aa6416d4826ec08008eac8947e42b005fbf9c446","tid":2223355,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T19:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0da3917441247af2318e1022d1c3c86cf5b8177","tid":2223355,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T19:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />現實係點心照啦"},{"pid":"7eda327a3986c5724d6bd607274ddceaad34ef0e","tid":2223355,"uid":155936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc